       Connie!                  

243
00:12:19,238 --> 00:12:21,706
        Aah!                    

244
00:12:21,741 --> 00:12:23,508
     [ Grunts ]                 

245
00:12:23,543 --> 00:12:25,143
             I know this sword. 

246
00:12:25,178 --> 00:12:29,313
              This is the sword 
             that shattered her!

247
00:12:29,348 --> 00:12:30,848
      [ Gasps ]                 

248
00:12:30,883 --> 00:12:32,550
              Aah!              

249
00:12:33,886 --> 00:12:36,988
        [ People crying ]       

250
00:12:37,023 --> 00:12:40,825
             You deserve this --
                 all of you!    

251
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:42,827
          Stop, please!         

252
00:12:42,862 --> 00:12:45,329
                      Steven!   
 What do we do?!                

253
00:12:45,364 --> 00:12:48,766
 I don't know. She won't listen,
    she just wants to fight.    

254
00:12:48,801 --> 00:12:51,536
Garnet: Blue Diamond!           

255
00:12:53,406 --> 00:12:56,374
                 Who are you    
               supposed to be?  

256
00:12:56,409 --> 00:12:59,577
I am the will of two gems       
to care for each other,         

257
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:01,946
to protect each other           
  from any threat,              

258
00:13:01,981 --> 00:13:04,315
 no matter how vast             
    or how cruel.               

259
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:09,187
You couldn't stop me 5,750 years
ago, and you can't stop me now! 

260
00:13:09,222 --> 00:13:14,725
It's you, that Ruby and Sapphire
        that disrupted my court.

261
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,194
        Ugh!                    

262
00:13:16,229 --> 00:13:18,129
 This is supposed to            
     be my day!                 

263
00:13:18,164 --> 00:13:22,166
           You hope to defeat me
         by clinging to my feet?

264
00:13:22,201 --> 00:13:25,803
I just needed to keep you from  
taking three steps to the right.

265
00:13:25,838 --> 00:13:34,312
                     ♪♪         

266
00:13:34,347 --> 00:13:35,914
             What?!             

267
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,487
                   Whoo...      

268
00:13:43,522 --> 00:13:45,656
       Lapis?!                  

269
00:13:45,691 --> 00:13:47,058
[ Breathing heavily ]           

270
00:13:47,093 --> 00:13:49,427
 You're really here.            

271
00:13:49,462 --> 00:13:50,661
                    Hey.        

272
00:13:50,696 --> 00:13:52,230
             Lapis!             

273
00:13:52,265 --> 00:13:54,832
     You came back -- again!    

274
00:13:54,867 --> 00:13:56,534
           I couldn't stay away.

275
00:13:56,569 --> 00:13:59,170
      If they're gonna punish me
             like a crystal gem,

276
00:13:59,205 --> 00:14:01,772
         I might as well be one,
                   right?       

277
00:14:01,807 --> 00:14:03,774
                You got room    
                for one more?   

278
00:14:03,809 --> 00:14:05,209
           Of course!           

279
00:14:05,244 --> 00:14:06,944
        Save the hugs for       
        after the fight.        

280
00:14:06,979 --> 00:14:08,379
           Look alive!          

281
00:14:09,849 --> 00:14:12,183
          Lapis Lazuli!         

282
00:14:12,218 --> 00:14:15,953
    Does every gem that comes   
   in contact with this planet  

283
00:14:15,988 --> 00:14:18,423
         turn traitor?!         

284
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:21,959
              What?             

285
00:14:21,994 --> 00:14:25,997
  I've felt worse.              

286
00:14:29,835 --> 00:14:31,535
       Knock her off this beach!

287
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:33,571
        Now's our chance!       

288
00:14:33,606 --> 00:14:37,475
                     ♪♪         

289
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:40,478
 With all our strength together,
      we can take her down!     

290
00:14:40,513 --> 00:14:43,180
          That's right!         
       This is our home...      

291
00:14:43,215 --> 00:14:46,217
          our planet...         
     our friends and family!    

292
00:14:46,252 --> 00:14:49,220
    We are the Crystal Gems!    

293
00:14:49,255 --> 00:14:53,491
            Pathetic!           
        You are nothing!        

294
00:14:53,526 --> 00:15:05,803
                     ♪♪         

295
00:15:05,838 --> 00:15:09,807
                     ♪♪         

296
00:15:09,842 --> 00:15:11,609
            [ Roars ]           

297
00:15:11,644 --> 00:15:17,448
                     ♪♪         

298
00:15:17,483 --> 00:15:19,984
            Wah-ahh!            

299
00:15:21,053 --> 00:15:23,654
       Hey, Blue diamond,       
            fight me!           

300
00:15:23,689 --> 00:15:27,391
             You got guts, tiny!
         Let me give you a hand!

301
00:15:27,426 --> 00:15:31,028
              Wha!              

302
00:15:31,063 --> 00:15:33,531
       Everyone, group up!      

303
00:15:33,566 --> 00:15:45,977
                     ♪♪         

304
00:15:46,012 --> 00:15:51,549
                     ♪♪         

305
00:15:51,584 --> 00:15:53,351
        Yeah!                   

306
00:15:53,386 --> 00:16:03,594
                     ♪♪         

307
00:16:03,629 --> 00:16:06,130
     [ Electricity zapping ]    

308
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,134
                  Uh, guys?     

309
00:16:13,739 --> 00:16:15,907
                 Run for it!    

310
00:16:17,376 --> 00:16:19,477
              Aah!              

311
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,446
     The house!                 

312
00:16:22,481 --> 00:16:24,015
          Don't worry,          
          I can fix it!         

313
00:16:24,050 --> 00:16:26,517
                         My dad!
            Uh-oh...            

314
00:16:26,552 --> 00:16:29,620
           All right,           
   I'm stickin' with you guys!  

315
00:16:29,655 --> 00:16:31,856
            [ Thud ]            

316
00:16:31,891 --> 00:16:34,025
              Hup!              

317
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:36,861
 Did we do it?                  
          [ All gasp ]          

318
00:16:38,931 --> 00:16:41,966
      Cluster, you were amazing!
                Are you okay?   

319
00:16:42,001 --> 00:16:44,035
          Do you want to go back
               in your bubble?  

320
00:16:45,104 --> 00:16:48,506
             Okay, take it easy!
              You're the best.  

321
00:16:50,209 --> 00:16:53,244
     So, that is                
a wedding reception.            

322
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:55,813
   Hmm. Nice job,               
  wedding planner.              

323
00:16:55,848 --> 00:16:59,183
  Did ya see that?!             
She couldn't lay a finger on me!

324
00:16:59,218 --> 00:17:00,584
         Hmm, but did you notice

325
00:17:00,619 --> 00:17:03,120
         how I perfectly managed
              my trajectory --  

326
00:17:03,155 --> 00:17:04,922
           right into her eyes?!

327
00:17:04,957 --> 00:17:06,957
              I'll demonstrate! 
              Launch me again!  

328
00:17:06,992 --> 00:17:10,361
    [ Chuckles ] I like you,    
    Peridot. You don't quit.    

329
00:17:11,464 --> 00:17:13,330
          [ Clanging ]          

330
00:17:13,365 --> 00:17:25,009
                     ♪♪         

331
00:17:26,912 --> 00:17:29,480
                     Ha!        
            I told her off once.

332
00:17:29,515 --> 00:17:30,948
             I can do it again! 

333
00:17:30,983 --> 00:17:33,884
  Hey, yellow clod!             

334
00:17:33,919 --> 00:17:36,387
    Remember me?!               

335
00:17:36,422 --> 00:17:38,389
               No.              

336
00:17:43,262 --> 00:17:45,629
        Stop!                   
   Don't do this!!              

337
00:17:45,664 --> 00:17:47,832
   Listen to me --              
I'm the one you're missing!     

338
00:17:47,867 --> 00:17:49,633
  I'm Pink Diamond!             

339
00:17:49,668 --> 00:17:51,102
              You!              

340
00:17:52,571 --> 00:17:54,172
        Aah!                    

341
00:17:55,007 --> 00:17:56,607
             Steven!            

342
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,646
                  Steven?!      

343
00:18:02,681 --> 00:18:03,848
       Steven:                  
Connie, what's wrong?!          

344
00:18:03,883 --> 00:18:05,816
                  Come on,      
               please wake up!  

345
00:18:05,851 --> 00:18:08,419
   I'm up, I'm up!              
  What's going on?!             

346
00:18:08,454 --> 00:18:10,855
Connie, I'm right here!         

347
00:18:10,890 --> 00:18:13,023
              Come on, Steven,  
                we need you!    

348
00:18:13,058 --> 00:18:15,693
        Aah!                    
 What the hoo-hah?!             

349
00:18:15,728 --> 00:18:17,094
        Huh.                    

350
00:18:17,129 --> 00:18:19,530
 Well, this is new.             

351
00:18:19,565 --> 00:18:22,333
 What is this place?            

352
00:18:22,368 --> 00:18:29,607
                     ♪♪         

353
00:18:29,642 --> 00:18:33,711
    What else have you got?!    
 I've only just begun to fight! 

354
00:18:33,746 --> 00:18:36,614
              Aah!              

355
00:18:36,649 --> 00:18:37,815
  [ Gasps ] Lapis!              

356
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:42,820
                     ♪♪         

357
00:18:42,855 --> 00:18:44,555
       Connie,                  
are you seeing this?!           

358
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:46,657
              Wake up! Please!  

359
00:18:46,692 --> 00:18:49,894
   <i> We're supposed to be in this</i>
            <i> together, remember?</i>

360
00:18:49,929 --> 00:18:52,630
     Uh, Connie, I'm o-kay?     

361
00:18:52,665 --> 00:18:54,899
    Huh? Steven?!               

362
00:18:54,934 --> 00:18:57,835
     Huh?                       
               Connie, it's me! 

363
00:18:57,870 --> 00:19:00,137
  W-where are you?              
How are you doing...            

364
00:19:00,172 --> 00:19:01,505
       I'm not sure, but I think

365
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:03,807
          it's a classic psychic
           ghost-type situation!

366
00:19:03,842 --> 00:19:05,776
   Ah, of course.               

367
00:19:05,811 --> 00:19:07,511
So, what's the plan?            

368
00:19:07,546 --> 00:19:09,246
 The diamonds won't listen to me
                 out there,     

369
00:19:09,281 --> 00:19:11,348
     but maybe I can get through
                to them here.   

370
00:19:11,383 --> 00:19:14,018
 They've gotta know Pink Diamond
              wasn't shattered. 

371
00:19:14,053 --> 00:19:16,287
          Please protect my body
               while I'm gone.  

372
00:19:16,322 --> 00:19:19,190
       Got it!                  
Good luck out there, Steven.    

373
00:19:19,225 --> 00:19:24,495
                     ♪♪         

374
00:19:24,530 --> 00:19:27,031
         This is it, I've got to
              hold it together. 

375
00:19:27,066 --> 00:19:28,799
               I've gotta hold  
             everyone together. 

376
00:19:28,834 --> 00:19:32,937
     You can do it, Garnet!     
 Remember, you're made of love! 

377
00:19:32,972 --> 00:19:34,705
       Steven?                  

378
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:37,541
        <i> Huh.</i>                   
<i> Always full of surprises.</i>      

379
00:19:37,576 --> 00:19:40,010
    [ Grunting ]                

380
00:19:40,045 --> 00:19:42,379
      Amethyst:                 
<i>Don't get shattered, don't get</i>  
<i>shattered, don't get shattered!</i> 

381
00:19:42,414 --> 00:19:44,682
   You can do this, Amethyst!   
        I believe in you!       

382
00:19:44,717 --> 00:19:46,150
      <i> Steven?</i>                  

383
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:48,819
<i> I can do this! I can do this!</i>  
   <i> I can do this!</i>              

384
00:19:49,655 --> 00:19:52,656
       Pearl:                   
<i> I won't give up! Everything</i>    
<i> I do, I do it for her!</i>         

385
00:19:52,691 --> 00:19:54,124
  <i> I do it for him!</i>             

386
00:19:54,159 --> 00:19:55,893
  Don't forget about yourself,  
             Pearl!             

387
00:19:55,928 --> 00:19:57,828
  <i> I do it for me!</i>              

388
00:19:58,597 --> 00:20:03,234
<i>I just got my friends back, and</i> 
   <i> now I'm gonna lose em again?</i>

389
00:20:03,269 --> 00:20:06,203
     We can still do this --    
            together!           

390
00:20:06,238 --> 00:20:09,540
<i> What am I thinking!</i>            
<i> We haven't lost yet!</i>           

391
00:20:10,943 --> 00:20:14,111
     Hang in there, Peridot.    
        You, too, Lapis!        

392
00:20:16,515 --> 00:20:17,881
           [ Grunts ]           

393
00:20:17,916 --> 00:20:22,386
                     ♪♪         

394
00:20:22,421 --> 00:20:26,023
   <i> How miserable. I knew Pink</i>  
<i>couldn't handle her own colony,</i> 

395
00:20:26,058 --> 00:20:28,058
         but I gave in.         

396
00:20:28,093 --> 00:20:30,728
      <i> And now I'm to blame</i>     
         <i> for her fate.</i>         

397
00:20:30,763 --> 00:20:32,896
              Aah!              

398
00:20:32,931 --> 00:20:34,865
  Her thoughts are too strong!  

399
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:37,868
     <i> What good</i>                 
<i> will any of this do?</i>           

400
00:20:37,903 --> 00:20:40,070
<i> The more I make these gems</i>     
      <i> suffer,</i>                  

401
00:20:40,105 --> 00:20:42,873
<i> the more I long to see you</i>     
    <i> again, Pink.</i>               

402
00:20:42,908 --> 00:20:44,842
              Huh?              

403
00:20:44,877 --> 00:20:51,282
                     ♪♪         

404
00:20:51,317 --> 00:20:53,584
             Almost!            

405
00:20:53,619 --> 00:20:55,853
  Blue Diamond, please listen!  

406
00:20:55,888 --> 00:20:57,621
           Whoa, whoa!          

407
00:20:57,656 --> 00:20:59,423
                What the...?    

408
00:20:59,458 --> 00:21:02,226
 I felt something --            
      someone.                  

409
00:21:02,261 --> 00:21:05,062
                 It worked!     
    I gotta get through to them!

410
00:21:05,097 --> 00:21:08,565
                    Ahh!        

411
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,901
              Pink isn't gone!  
        I can explain everything

412
00:21:10,936 --> 00:21:12,736
              if you just stop  
               this fighting!   

413
00:21:12,771 --> 00:21:14,972
                        Aah!    
       There it is again!       

414
00:21:15,007 --> 00:21:16,807
    What are you                
  jabbering about?              

415
00:21:16,842 --> 00:21:19,410
                 A presence!    
              It feels like...  

416
00:21:19,445 --> 00:21:22,680
          Please, Blue,         
    you're being hysterical,    

417
00:21:22,715 --> 00:21:24,248
       more so than usual.      

418
00:21:24,283 --> 00:21:26,917
Listen, Yellow, Pink's fate     
is different than you think!    

419
00:21:26,952 --> 00:21:29,019
She faked her shattering!       

420
00:21:29,054 --> 00:21:31,689
                This feeling,   
                 I know it!     

421
00:21:31,724 --> 00:21:33,157
       It must be a trick!      

422
00:21:33,192 --> 00:21:34,758
       Show yourself, foe!      

423
00:21:34,793 --> 00:21:36,093
  I'm not your foe!             

424
00:21:36,128 --> 00:21:38,062
Please just listen to me!       

425
00:21:38,097 --> 00:21:39,530
           There! Aah.          

426
00:21:39,565 --> 00:21:40,731
        Aah!                    

427
00:21:40,766 --> 00:21:46,036
                     ♪♪         

428
00:21:46,071 --> 00:21:48,539
         Steven: Please,        
    the fighting has to stop.   

429
00:21:48,574 --> 00:21:51,208
       We aren't enemies,       
          we're family.         

430
00:21:51,243 --> 00:21:53,043
      Please, listen to me!     

431
00:21:53,078 --> 00:21:57,114
       I need you to know       
            who I am!           

432
00:21:58,417 --> 00:21:59,783
           Impossible!          

433
00:21:59,818 --> 00:22:01,318
          This aura...          

434
00:22:01,353 --> 00:22:07,558
                     ♪♪         

435
00:22:11,497 --> 00:22:12,730
            [ Gasps ]           

436
00:22:12,765 --> 00:22:15,399
                  It's you!     

437
00:22:15,434 --> 00:22:16,867
                    Pink!       

438
00:22:18,804 --> 00:22:20,704
                     ♪♪         

439
00:22:20,739 --> 00:22:23,374
      ♪ I always thought ♪      

440
00:22:23,409 --> 00:22:25,042
       ♪ I might be bad ♪       

441
00:22:25,077 --> 00:22:28,812
 ♪ Now I'm sure that it's true ♪

442
00:22:28,847 --> 00:22:32,883
        ♪ 'Cause I think        
        you're so good ♪        

